| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `GET` | Get single requirement with submission stats |
| `PUT` | Update requirement (title, description, scope, deadline) |
| `DELETE` | Soft-delete (set `is_active: false`) |

---

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/submissions/route.ts)

| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `GET` | List all submissions (filterable by requirement, student, status, batch) |

---

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/submissions/[id]/review/route.ts)

| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `PUT` | Approve or reject a submission with optional comment |

---

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/submissions/[id]/download/route.ts)

| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `GET` | Securely download a student's uploaded file (streams from Cloudinary) |

---

### Student API Layer

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/documents/route.ts)

| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `GET` | List all requirements applicable to this student (with their submission status) |

The API resolves which requirements apply by checking:
1. `scope.type === 'all'` вҶ’ applies to everyone
2. `scope.type === 'program'` вҶ’ student's program matches
3. `scope.type === 'batch'` вҶ’ student's batch matches
4. `scope.type === 'student'` вҶ’ student's ID is in the list

---

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/documents/upload/route.ts)

| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `POST` | Upload a file for a specific requirement (Cloudinary `raw` upload) |

Validates: file size, file type matches requirement, student is in scope, requirement is active and not past due.

---

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/documents/[id]/resubmit/route.ts)

| Method | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `PUT` | Re-upload after rejection (old file archived in `submission_history`) |

---

### Admin UI

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(admin)/admin/documents/page.tsx)

Two-tab admin page:

**Tab 1 вҖ” Requirements:**
- Create/edit requirement form (title, description, category, scope assignment, file types, deadline)
- Table listing all requirements with filters
- Delete (soft) requirements

**Tab 2 вҖ” Submissions:**
- Table of all student submissions with filters (by requirement, batch, status)
- Each row shows: student name, requirement title, submitted file, status badge, date
- Click row вҶ’ side panel with: file preview/download, approve/reject buttons, comment field
- Bulk approve option

---

### Student UI

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(student)/student/documents/page.tsx)

Student documents dashboard:
- Cards grouped by category (Personal Documents, Assignments, Academic, Certificates)
- Each card shows: requirement title, status badge (Pending/Approved/Rejected/Not Submitted), due date
- Upload button вҶ’ opens file upload modal
- For rejected documents: shows rejection reason + re-upload button

